Release 0.5.0 - 24/08/2006:

	* Add debian package
	* Improve support for canceling coupons.
	* Require kiwi 1.9.6
	* Updated translation

Release 0.4.0 - 24/08/2006:

	* Bug fixes: 2502, 2532, 2641

	* Metrologic MC630 Barcode reader support
	* Test suite implemented
	* Implementation of a virtual port for drivers which doesn't requires
	  communication with a real device (eg, VirtualSimple driver).

Release 0.3.1 - 02/07/2006:

	* Bug fixes: 2246, 2531, 2628

	* Include support for driver constants
	* Fiscal printer API improved
	* pt_BR translation

Release 0.3.0 - 08/03/2006:

	* Bug fixes: 700, 2153, 2274, 2362, 2369, 2383,
		     2386, 2408, 2441

	* Exception strings internationalization
	* Better error management for Bematech MP25 driver
	* Till cash out support
	* Better text encoding management on printer command parameters
	* Bematech DP20C printer support
	* Custom product unit support
	* Toledo Prix III scale support

Release 0.2.0 - 22/12/2005:

	* Bug fixes: 2125, 2149, 2158, 2176, 2240, 2248, 
		     2280, 2284, 2328, 2346

	* Driver capabilities implementation.
	* Dataregis EP375 support.
	* PertoPay 2023 support.
	* Virtual printer implementation.

Release 0.1.0 - 26/09/2005

	* Bug fixes: 2131, 2132, 2133, 2148, 2155, 2156

	* Standard exceptions management implemented.
	* Daruma FS2100 support.
	* Support for multiple printer models of the same manufacter.
	* Installation script implementation.
	* Support for items cancellation on Daruma FS345.
